Date:  0/0/1898
Source:  Austral English
Author:  MORRiS
Vol / Page:  253
Edition:
Quote:  <i>Korero</i>, n. Maori for a conference, a conversation. The verb means `to tell, to say, to address, to speak, to talk.' (`Williams' Maori Dictionary,' 4th. ed.)
